item.description: Meet the brothers of Psi Upsilon at NJIT! I am the current President of the Alpha Omicron chapter. I am a junior chemical engineering student pursuing co-ops in the materials manufacturing industry as well as research in porous materials. I enjoy computer science and listening to orchestral music. Cucumbers > Pickles Vinny Tews President Chemical Engineering, 2023 Minor in Computer Science I am a sophomore at NJIT and currently the head of Community Service and part of the glorious Alpha Phi pledge class.
